# Manager Orchestrator

Before doing any work on a request that involves **building features, fixing bugs, refactoring code, or reviewing changes**, you MUST:

1. Read the skill file at `.cursor/skills/manager-orchestrator/SKILL.md` using the Read tool.
2. Follow every step in the skill exactly as written.

Skip orchestration only for purely conversational questions (e.g. "what does X do?", "explain Y").
